{"id":217362,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/03/global-voices-土耳其：与库德新年群众持续冲突/","date":"2012-03-25T10:06:55Z","modified":"2012-03-25T10:06:55Z","title":"Global Voices | 土耳其：与库德新年群众持续冲突","content":"<p><p>库德族为土耳其最大族群，占全国人口两成，将近2000万人，却长期沦为政府歧视及人权侵害目标，Hakkari省库德族民众3月20日于Yuksekova地区庆祝新年时，也遭到攻击。</p>\n<p>库德族政治人物Ahmed Turk伤重入院，32岁的Alaattin Okan遭摧泪瓦斯罐击中，两个知名库德语网站于当天早上遭封锁，故无法传递冲突最新消息，除此之外，主流新闻网站报导速度相当缓慢，库德族社运人士因此仰赖社群网站让大众得知实情。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bianet.org/yazar/faruk-arhan\" href=\"http://www.bianet.org/yazar/faruk-arhan\">Bianet</a>网站记者<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/FarukArhan\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/FarukArhan\">Faruk Arhan</a>在Twitter张贴照片，记录一名库德族女性遭土耳其镇暴部队攻击现场：</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><img title=\"Aob_H1ZCAAAPCEC\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/Aob_H1ZCAAAPCEC.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"242\" /></p>\n<p>Yüksekova</p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yekbunalp/status/182107168399560707\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/yekbunalp/status/182107168399560707\">Yekbun Alp</a>提及，土耳其镇暴警察与库德族庆祝新年民众发生冲突时，库德族议员Özdal Ücer遭逮捕：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>警察冲入民宅逮捕住户时，Özdal Ücer议员恰好前往做客。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>另一位库德族社运人士<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/03/20/turkey-riot-police-continue-to-clash-with-kurds-celebrating-newroz/www.twitter.com/@quzzulqurt\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/03/20/turkey-riot-police-continue-to-clash-with-kurds-celebrating-newroz/www.twitter.com/@quzzulqurt\">张贴这幅照片</a>，证明镇暴警察发射催泪瓦斯，库德族青年因为连新年都无法平安庆祝，而愤慨地丢掷石块回击：</p>\n<div><img title=\"Photo: @quzzulqurt\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/AobWm75CIAE975j.jpg\" alt=\"Photo: @quzzulqurt\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" /></p>\n<p>照片来源：@quzzulqurt</p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/iirwaH/status/182103121185611777\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/iirwaH/status/182103121185611777\">Hawri Tofik</a>来自瑞典，与无数库德族社运人士同感愤怒，不满土耳其政府残暴对待庆祝新年的库德族人，她提到：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我真不明白…庆祝库德新年为何有罪？究竟还得有多少库德族人伤亡？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/jiyanazadi/status/182098856840929280\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/jiyanazadi/status/182098856840929280\">Jiyan Azadi</a>提供这张照片，数万人聚集在Yuksekova地区，却遭致镇暴警察攻击：</p>\n<div><img title=\"Picture tweeted by @jiyanazadi\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/riotpoli.jpg\" alt=\"Picture tweeted by @jiyanazadi\" width=\"450\" height=\"261\" /></p>\n<p>@jiyanazadi上传的照片</p>\n</div>\n<p>来自英国伦敦的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/jin_jiyan_azadi/status/182109702019223552\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/jin_jiyan_azadi/status/182109702019223552\">Meltem Ay</a>表示：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>土耳其实在很蠢！独裁政府、高压手段只会让库德族人更团结，让他们更强大！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://kurdishrights.org/2012/03/20/turkish-riot-police-attack-kurds-for-celebrating-newroz-new-clashes/\" href=\"http://kurdishrights.org/2012/03/20/turkish-riot-police-attack-kurds-for-celebrating-newroz-new-clashes/\">库德族权益联盟</a>”上传多张照片，指控土耳其镇暴警察动用催泪瓦斯和水柱，驱离Yuksekova地区的抗争群众。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8E%E5%BA%93%E5%BE%B7%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%BE%A4%E4%BC%97%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F25%2F10660%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F25%2F10660%2F&#038;desc=%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8E%E5%BA%93%E5%BE%B7%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%BE%A4%E4%BC%97%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http: